    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hello! I just tried this recipe and they taste great, but I have a question! Did yours maintain it&#39;s shape quite well and how is this achieved? I&#39;ve made so many batches and I love scalloped edge cookies but they keep coming out funny! 🙁 Please help! Thank you xx</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-9724" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
